---
title: Payment Processing Flow
config:
  theme: neutral
  look: classic
---
sequenceDiagram
  %% Legend: blue=request, green=success, red=error/timeout
  
  box Payment Processing Scope
    participant Client as Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway
    participant Processor as Processor
  end

  Client->>|"request"| Gateway: Submit payment
  Gateway->>|"authorize"| Processor: Check payment
  
  alt Success
    Processor-->>|"approve"| Gateway: Card valid
    Gateway-->>|"confirm"| Client: Token issued
  else Declined
    Processor-->>|"decline"| Gateway: Card rejected
    Gateway-->>|"error"| Client: Payment failed
  else Expired
    Processor-->>|"expired"| Gateway: Card expired
    Gateway-->>|"error"| Client: Expired card
  else Timeout
    Processor--x|"timeout"| Gateway: No response
    Gateway-->>|"error"| Client: Service timeout
  end

  Note over Client,Gateway: Scope: Payment initiation through settlement


